CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1959, pg. 18 reads: " "Bohemian" Party - These boys and girls were guests at a "Bohemian" supper and party given by Carol Bush, Dec. 30. Among those who attended were Kenny Hudson, Alvinia Holt, Azalee Spencer, Joe Golden, Oliver Jackson, Virginia Haley, Jake Milliones, Beverly White and Miss Bush. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of young men and young women, including Kenny Hudson, Alvinia Holt, Azalee Spencer, Joe Golden, Oliver Jackson, Virginia Haley, Jake Milliones, Beverly White, and Carol Bush, gathered for party in domestic interior, possibly Bush residence, with dark sofa, lamp, and plant, another version
